-shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">app</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"space\"> </span><span class=\"space\"> </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">h1</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">{{ store.count }}</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;/</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">h1</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;/</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">div</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><p>预览并查看页面即可。</p>\n<div class=\"demo-wrapper no-padding\">\n  <div class=\"demo-head\">\n    <div class=\"demo-ctrl\"><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>\n    \n  </div>\n  <div class=\"demo-container\" >\n<div style=\"text-align:center\"><p><img src=\"https://ccccooh.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20250226193628.png\" alt=\"20250226193628\"></p>\n</div></div></div>","tagOpen":"<template>","tagClose":"</template>"},"script":null,"scriptSetup":null,"scripts":[],"styles":[],"customBlocks":[]},"content":"## 工程化项目中的安装\n\n如果是通过脚手架搭建的项目可以通过`NPM`或者`Yarn`安装到项目当中：\n\n::: npm-to\n```sh\nnpm install pinia\n```\n:::\n\n## CDN 方式引入与使用\n\n如果没有使用脚手架的项目也可以通过CDN来引入 `Pinia`的js文件来使用。\n\n**项目结构**：\n::: file-tree\n- pinia1\n  - js\n  - lib\n    - **pinia.min.js** # pinia 文件\n    - vueDemi.js # 一款开发工具。允许你为 Vue 2 和 3 编写通用 Vue 库。而无需担心用户安装的版本。\n    - vue.min.js # Vue3 文件\n:::\n\n接着在`pinial1`下创建一个`index.html`文件。\n\n使用`!`生成模板后引入js文件：\n```html\n<script src=\"./lib/vue.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"./lib/vueDemi.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"./lib/pinia.min.js\"></script>\n```\n\n使用`createPinia()`来将其注入到Vue实例中：\n```html\n...\n<div id=\"app\"></div>\n...\n<script type=\"module\">\n  // 创建 Vue 实例\n  const app = Vue.createApp({\n    setup() {},\n  });\n  // 注入 Pinia 对象\n  app.use(createPinia());\n  app.mount(\"#app\");\n</script>\n```\n\n接下来创建一个`store`文件：\n::: code-tabs\n@tab js/store.js\n```js\nconst { defineStore } = Pinia; // 引入 defineStore 函数\n// 创建 id=counter 的 store\nconst useCounterStore = defineStore(\"counter\", {\n  state: () => ({\n    count: 10, // 声明一个 state count 并初始化为 10\n  }),\n  getters: {},\n  actions: {},\n});\n```\n:::\n\n在上述代码中创建了一个`state`, `count`被赋值为10。\n\n之后，在`index.html`中引入`store.js`文件:\n```js\n<script src=\"./lib/vue.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"./lib/vueDemi.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"./lib/pinia.min.js\"></script>\n<!--  引入 store 文件 -->\n<script src=\"./js/store.js\"></script>\n```\n\n在`index.html`中调用`store.js`文件的`useCounterStore`方法获取`store`对象`couter`，并把该对象在Vue的`setup()`中返回：\n```html\n<script type=\"module\">\n    const { createApp } = Vue\n    const { createPinia } = Pinia\n    const app = Vue.createApp({ // 创建 Vue 实例对象 app\n       setup() {\n        const store = useCounterStore(); // 调用 useCounterStore 方法获取 store 对象 counter\n          return {\n            store // 返回 store 对象，方便 DOM 中使用\n          }\n        }\n    });\n    app.use(createPinia()) // 将 pinia 插件用于 Vue 实例对象 app 中\n    app.mount('#app');\n</script>\n```\n\n在DOM结构中：\n```html\n<div id=\"app\">\n  <h1>{{ store.count }}</h1>\n</div>\n```\n\n预览并查看页面即可。\n\n:::: demo-wrapper no-padding\n::: center\n![20250226193628](https://ccccooh.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20250226193628.png)\n:::\n::::","excerpt":"","includedFiles":[],"tasklistId":0,"title":"","headers":[{"level":2,"title":"工程化项目中的安装","slug":"工程化项目中的安装","link":"#工程化项目中的安装","children":[]},{"level":2,"title":"CDN 方式引入与使用","slug":"cdn-方式引入与使用","link":"#cdn-方式引入与使用","children":[]}]}}
